  "title": "Dishwasher/ Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for dishwashers/cleaners to be part of our kitchen team</p><p><strong>5.5 days Week</strong></p><p><strong>Monday to Friday: 10.30am - 3pm / Break / 6pm - 11pm 周日休息日</strong></p><p><strong>Saturday: 6pm - 11pm</strong></p><p><strong>Sunday OFF Day</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Cleaner</p><p>职责：</p><p>• 刮、冲洗并将盘子和器皿装入洗碗机</p><p>• 清洗和消毒所有平底锅、锅、器皿和盘子</p><p>• 清洁、消毒和维护洗碗机</p><p>• 从洗碗机卸下盘子和餐具并妥善整理</p><p>• 定期清空垃圾箱</p><p>• 根据需要清扫和拖地，保持工作区和厨房清洁</p><p>• 根据要求执行额外的清洁任务</p><p>• 清洁和维护客用浴室</p><p>• 清洁食品准备站和设备</p><p><br /></p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>• Scrape, rinse, and load dishes and utensils into dish machine</p><p>• Wash and sanitize all pans, pots, utensils, and dishes</p><p>• Clean, sanitize, and maintain dish machine</p><p>• Unload dishes and utensils from dish machine and organize them properly</p><p>• Empty trash containers regularly</p><p>• Maintain a clean work area and kitchen by sweeping and mopping as needed</p><p>• Perform additional cleaning duties as requested</p><p>• Clean and mantain Guest Bathroom</p><p>• Clean food prep stations and equipment</p>",
